ssian). Include existing facts and new. Should be concise, 1-3 sentences. Let's craft about Znayka: He participated, traveled to Moon, discovered brick wall, etc., proposed hypothesis about ancient fiery liquid surface, explained that heated liquid inside Moon cools and contracts, published book, invited to academy, often says "Верно!". Keep within 1-3 sentences. Maybe two sentences.

